<bibRefCitation author="Hughes, Lauren E." journalOrPublisher="Journal of Crustacean Biology" pageId="0" pageNumber="28937" pagination="699 - 709" title="Establishing a neotype for Elasmopusrapax Costa, 1853 and its presence as an invasive species in temperate Australian waters" volume="30" year="2010">Hughes and Lowry 2010</bibRefCitation>
